Package: zen-c
Version: 1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, make, clang, llvm
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/z-libs/Zen-C
Description: High-level Systems Programming Language compiling to C
 Zen-C is a modern systems programming language that compiles to
 human-readable GNU C/C11. Provides type inference, pattern matching,
 generics, traits, async/await, and manual memory management with
 RAII while maintaining 100% C ABI compatibility.
